'''Baharestan''' ({{lang-fa|بهارستان}} lit. "The Spring Garden") is an [[Iran]]ian newspaper in the [[Fars province|Fars]] region. The [[Concessionaire]] of this newspaper was ''Habibollah Noubakht'' and it was published in [[Shiraz]] since 1920.<ref>Rumi,Siroos; List of printed matters of Fars;2006;[[Ministry of Culture and Islamic Guidance (Iran)]]</ref>

